O '''indekso le manushutne baryaripnasko''' si labyardo tar e [[Phandle Naciye]], ginindoi o [[chhoripen]], [[lekhavipnsko janglipen]], [[jivipnasko shaipen]] thai aver zorale butya [[them]]endar. O kamipen si te ginel o [[jivipnasko mishtipen]]. But manusha labyaren les te te janen kana ekh them si andar i ekhto, duito vai trito lumya.

O indekso kerdilo [[1990]] bersheste, tar o [[pakistan]]o [[Mahbub ul Haq]] thay sas labyardo tar o [[Baryaripnasko Programo le Phandle Naciyengo]] (katar [[1993]]) ando bershutno [[Reporto le Manushtne Baryaripnasko]].

Kana kerel pes o indekso, le mai zorale butya so si ginyarde si:
* ekh lungo thai sasto jivipen, palal o jivipnasko shaipen
* o lekhavipnsko janglipen thai o shkolyako phiripen
* dosta love te jivel mishto, palal o [[andrutno bruto produkto]] (ABP) kai [[komparativi kidipnaski zor]] (KKZ).


